1
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:02,600
All right.

2
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,640
Are you Mr. Qi Yi,

3
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,480
who made an appointment to visit Jingdezhen

4
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,880
Ceramic University Museum today?

5
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:08,800
Yes, I am.

6
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:10,560
I am Lin Yuexin,

7
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,520
a freshman in Heritage Conservation at Jingdezhen Ceramic University.

8
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:13,200
Today,

9
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,760
I will show you around.

10
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,200
If there's any dispute during the explanation,

11
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,530
my words shall prevail.

12
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,720
Then I'll leave it to you.

13
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:21,700
Please.

14
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,920
So why did you become

15
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,320
a museum guide?

16
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,759
I grew up in Jingdezhen.

17
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,800
I always wanted to go out and see the world,

18
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:41,360
so I applied for a culture and tourism major in college

19
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:41,920
and left.

20
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,940
After graduation,

21
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,940
I started working in a museum.

22
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:47,940
Then why did you come back?

23
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,060
The further away I was,

24
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,000
the more I missed home.

25
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,280
Later, I realized

26
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,479
that Jingdezhen is a

27
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,680
very charming place.

28
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,850
So I came back

29
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,440
and became a museum guide.

30
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,840
I hope more people

31
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,480
can learn about its history

32
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,410
and like it here.

33
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:07,860
What about you?

34
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:10,080
Why did you choose to come to Jingdezhen

35
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,940
and pick such an unpopular major?

36
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,600
When I was young,

37
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,400
my grandfather liked to collect antiques.

38
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,440
Among those antiques,

39
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,280
my favorites were the worn-out porcelains.

40
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,720
Every time I saw them,

41
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,600
I had a feeling

42
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,720
like I could see the stories

43
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,120
and origins behind them.

44
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,240
Later, I read in a book

45
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,690
that Jingdezhen

46
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,200
was their hometown.

47
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,200
So,

48
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,360
I came here.

49
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:44,050
I didn't expect you to be so action-oriented.

50
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:48,320
So many precious porcelains have been destroyed;

51
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:50,920
someone has to protect and restore them.

52
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,440
So,

53
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:54,600
I chose our major.

54
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:01,400
I think what you do is very meaningful.

55
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:02,880
Right?

56
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,200
I also really like

57
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,730
what we're doing right now,

58
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,640
and I've met a lot of like-minded friends.

59
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,320
For instance,

60
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,760
I met one recently.

61
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,960
Can you tell me about him?

62
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,400
You try one too.

63
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,839
Thank you.

64
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:36,730
Xiaocen.

65
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,330
When you have free time,

66
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,340
what do you usually like to do?

67
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:47,159
I usually stay at home when I'm off.

68
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,460
Is there anything you like doing?

69
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,320
Yes.

70
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,320
What is it?

71
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,880
When I'm at home,

72
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,800
I like playing chess with my mom.

73
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,450
Do you like going to the movies?

74
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,360
Because I think

75
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,440
the sound in the theater is too loud.

76
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,240
Then do you like listening to music?

77
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,920
If there's a concert,

78
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,600
would you want to go?

79
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,160
Yes.

80
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,820
But are there any concerts recently?

81
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,330
I don't think so.

82
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,200
Then is there anything recently

83
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,200
that you particularly like to eat,

84
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,800
or particularly want to eat?

85
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,280
Yes.

86
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:49,800
What?

87
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,400
My mom's cooking.

88
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,280
Is there anything

89
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:09,010
you want in particular lately?

90
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:16,720
No.

91
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:19,740
Any wishes?

92
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,760
World peace.

93
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,120
Xu Xiao,

94
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,680
what are you trying to say?

95
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,640
I just want to tell you

96
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,720
that I want to thank you

97
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,520
for everything you did for me.

98
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,360
For what?

99
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,120
About Zhang Jiatian and the porcelain.

100
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,320
About that, I...

101
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:54,640
You...

102
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,360
I...

103
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:55,840
I mean,

104
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,240
I know you helped me a lot.

105
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,440
Mr. Yue helped out the most with that.

106
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,600
True, Mr. Yue helped me,

107
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
and you helped me too.

108
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:00,920
For this,

109
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,560
I absolutely...

110
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,400
I really must thank you.

111
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,320
But I consider us friends.

112
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,380
This is important.

113
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,360
Yes, precisely because we are friends,

114
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,620
I especially need to thank you, you know?

115
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,120
I...

116
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:23,680
I...

117
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,320
I just don't know what to give you

118
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,520
to show my gratitude.

119
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,320
So...

120
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:34,140
Is there really nothing you want?

121
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:36,800
I...

122
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,520
I...

123
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,800
Let me think.

124
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,640
Let me think about it.

125
00:07:59,280 --> 00:07:59,680
Yes.

126
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,120
What?

127
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,000
What is it?

128
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,720
Can you

129
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,320
go somewhere with me?

130
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,480
Where to? Sure,

131
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,340
no problem.

132
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,760
Guyao Folk Customs Expo Area.

133
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,650
You want to go there?

134
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:16,880
I heard

135
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,880
you can see

136
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:22,040
ancient kilns from the Yuan and Ming dynasties there.

137
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,360
You can see the prosperity of

138
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,360
the Jingdezhen porcelain industry in the 15th and 16th centuries.

139
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:26,760
So,

140
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,600
I want to go check it out.

141
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,000
Sure.

142
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,680
I happen to be familiar with that area.

143
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,740
I can be your guide.

144
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:33,400
Really?

145
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,080
Great.

146
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,240
Is this

147
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,840
enough?

148
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:45,400
Enough.

149
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:47,720
Okay.

150
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,560
All right.

151
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,800
Relax.

152
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:16,440
Cheer up.

153
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,080
He'll be here in a minute.

154
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,080
Sister.

155
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,680
Why don't we leave?

156
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,560
I didn't want to come.

157
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,730
And I'm fine being alone right now.

158
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,440
I don't want a boyfriend.

159
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:28,920
Fine what?

160
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,160
Don't you know

161
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,360
that a broken family

162
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,920
has a huge impact on a child?

163
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,600
Look at Xiaoxing, isn't he doing fine?

164
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,920
You don't want to listen to me again, do you?

165
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,400
I'm telling you.

166
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,260
You didn't listen to me back then,

167
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,280
insisting on running away with that man

168
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,760
to get married in Jingdezhen.

169
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:43,620
And the result?

170
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:44,900
He ran away.

171
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,120
Leaving you and Xiaoxing alone.

172
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,560
You're a woman,

173
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,480
raising a child and working to make money.

174
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,680
How tired you must be.

175
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,880
I tell you,

176
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,560
the one I'm introducing you to this time

177
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,040
is a relative of my friend.

178
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,760
He was married before,

179
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,360
but then his wife

180
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,620
ran away with someone.

181
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,080
But he has no children.

182
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,320
I told him about your situation.

183
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,520
You know what he said?

184
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,400
He said

185
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,400
as long as you guys are suitable,

186
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,400
he can treat Xiaoxing

187
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,440
like his own child.

188
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,770
How rare is that?

189
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,080
Besides,

190
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,880
he has good conditions.

191
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,200
He works in the cultural industry.

192
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,200
He's quite rich.

193
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:21,240
Sister, I'm not short of money.

194
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,600
Not now, but what about the future?

195
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:27,560
Xiaoxing still needs to study, start a family, and get married.

196
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,840
How much money would that take?

197
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,040
Can you handle it alone?

198
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,720
Sister, you're going too far.

199
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,160
And all these things you mentioned

200
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,820
are Xiaoxing's own business.

201
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,120
What going too far?

202
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,200
I tell you, parents

203
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,960
should think further for their children.

204
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,440
I'm so sorry.

205
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,240
I'm sorry,

206
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:41,800
I'm late.

207
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,240
Get up.

208
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,680
Sorry.

209
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,480
Ms. Liu Qingfang?

210
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:46,280
Yes.

211
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:47,920
Mr. Zhang.

212
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,080
Zhang Hao.

213
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:49,600
Hello.

214
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:50,800
Hello.

215
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,280
This is my sister, Liu Qingying.

216
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,680
Hello, Zhang Hao.

217
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,080
Hello, Mr. Zhang.

218
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,040
Have a seat.

219
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,160
So, what would you like to drink?

220
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,720
What would you like to drink?

221
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,780
I'll have a coffee.

222
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:06,640
You want coffee too?

223
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,200
Coffee.

224
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,160
Waiter,

225
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,100
three coffees.

226
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,200
Okay, sir.

227
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:14,800
Mr. Zhang,

228
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,760
what have you been busy with lately?

229
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,400
Well,

230
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,940
you can just call me Zhang.

231
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,880
Can I call you Ms. Liu?

232
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,120
Of course.

233
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,200
I do a bit of business.

234
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,040
But recently, Jingdezhen's

235
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:28,880
cultural industry has been quite promising.

236
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,880
So I'm planning to enter this field.

237
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,560
Investing in some Jingdezhen drifters,

238
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:36,220
and building my own ceramic brand along the way.

239
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:39,920
I heard Ms. Liu Qingying is also in business.

240
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:42,080
What kind of big business do you do?

241
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,760
Not really.

242
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,180
I just run a small shop.

243
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,800
Running a small shop isn't easy.

244
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:48,160
And raising a child makes it even harder.

245
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,400
Not at all.

246
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,080
It's quite relaxing.

247
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,400
Here's the thing.

248
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,840
Our Xiaoxing

249
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,400
is very sensible and obedient.

250
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:57,880
So,

251
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,810
he hasn't caused her much trouble.

252
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,560
I actually like children myself.

253
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:02,400
That's great.

254
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:04,720
You really have the potential to be a good father.

255
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,800
I guess so.

256
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,240
Sir, your coffee.

257
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,740
The coffee is here.

258
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,520
Here you go.

259
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,880
Thank you.

260
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:11,880
Thanks.

261
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:12,540
No problem.

262
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,720
Let's see if we have a chance

263
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,720
to bring the kids out

264
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,920
and hang out together.

265
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,280
I know a place

266
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:23,760
where kids can make pottery.

267
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,020
The kids will definitely love it.

268
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,840
Let's talk about it later, Sis.

269
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,080
Let's do it tomorrow.

270
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,400
My daughter is off tomorrow.

271
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,080
She majors in ceramics.

272
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,320
It's a good chance for everyone to meet.

273
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,160
That's great.

274
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,200
Then tomorrow it is.

275
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,460
I'll arrange it, okay?

276
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,800
Okay, tomorrow.

277
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:44,360
Okay.

278
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:46,050
Come on, drink your coffee.

279
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,400
I'm back.

280
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:57,920
Xiaoxing, come out.

281
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,440
I'm not going.

282
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,880
Xiaoxing,

283
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:03,800
it will be so much fun making pottery together tomorrow.

284
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,520
And

285
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,120
an uncle will be joining you.

286
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,440
What uncle?

287
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,440
I don't want that.

288
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,120
Sister.

289
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,520
Maybe we shouldn't go.

290
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,920
I don't want to go either.

291
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,040
How can we do that?

292
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,640
We already promised him.

293
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:20,280
Xiaoxing,

294
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,440
open the door.

295
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:23,490
Mommy needs to tell you something.

296
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,690
I'll go in first.

297
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,130
I'll talk to him.

298
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,240
Okay, okay, okay.

299
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:32,200
Mom.

300
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:34,640
What's wrong with Xiaoxing?

301
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:36,100
He's spoiled by your aunt.

302
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,440
What's wrong?

303
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:44,040
Today,

304
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,240
I took your aunt on a blind date.

305
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,680
He's a great catch.

306
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:50,400
He works in the cultural industry.

307
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:52,000
So we made plans

308
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,860
for all of us to hang out tomorrow.

309
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,720
All of us?

310
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,000
Yes.

311
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:01,920
I have to go too?

312
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,680
Yes, I said all of us.

313
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:10,000
But I already have plans to hang out with my classmate tomorrow.

314
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,200
Then just cancel it.

315
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:14,170
I made the plans with my classmate a long time ago.

316
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,160
Then tell me, is your hanging out more important,

317
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,680
or your aunt's matter?

318
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:20,640
But...

319
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:21,800
But what?

320
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,240
Xiaoxing is immature,

321
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,760
are you going to be immature too?

322
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:25,620
Think about it,

323
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:28,240
how awkward would it be if only your aunt and Xiaoxing went?

324
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,400
If we all go together,

325
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:30,760
we can ease the tension.

326
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,000
Besides,

327
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,890
this concerns your aunt's future happiness.

328
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:44,560
Xu Xiao,

329
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,720
I'm sorry.

330
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,680
My mom needs me for something tomorrow,

331
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:50,880
so I can't go to the ancient kiln exhibition area with you.

332
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:51,680
Okay.

333
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,800
I'm sorry.

334
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:59,120
You haven't bought the tickets yet.

335
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,000
I didn't waste your money, did I?

336
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,720
I haven't bought them yet.

337
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,450
Don't worry.

338
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,880
Ms. Liu, Mr. Zhang.

339
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:25,480
Qingying.

340
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,570
You're here.

341
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,080
You must be Xiaoxing.

342
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:29,920
Yes, my son.

343
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,450
He's very handsome.

344
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:31,960
Hello.

345
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,360
Xiaoxing, call him Uncle.

346
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,220
Call him Uncle.

347
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:36,220
I won't.

348
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,000
You need to be polite.

349
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:40,760
It's fine.

350
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,720
He's just a kid.

351
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,000
Sorry about that.

352
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:43,780
No worries.

353
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,520
Oh, right.

354
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,160
This is my daughter, Xiaocen.

355
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:48,880
Hello, sir.

356
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:51,360
Ms. Liu, she takes after you.

357
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,560
Your whole family has such great genes.

358
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,560
Thank you, thank you.

359
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:56,820
Let's go inside first.

360
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:57,740
Let's go in.

361
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,290
Okay.

362
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:59,050
Let's go.

363
00:15:59,320 --> 00:15:59,650
Okay.

364
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,760
Come on, let's go.

365
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:02,370
Let's go.

366
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:06,440
Be careful not to get it on yourself.

367
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,340
What are you doing?

368
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,920
I'm working alone at the antique shop.

369
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:12,450
Xiaocen.

370
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:13,480
Mom.

371
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:14,720
What are you up to?

372
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,680
Nothing.

373
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,740
Sister Liu.

374
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:18,900
Aren't you joining us?

375
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:20,200
I won't play.

376
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,080
I'm going out to buy something.

377
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,760
Sis.

378
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,000
Don't just play.

379
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,400
Talk to each other and get to know each other better.

380
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:27,060
You hear me?

381
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,800
Have fun then.

382
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,080
Okay.

383
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,340
I'll be back in a while.

384
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:30,800
Okay.

385
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,330
Keep an eye on Xiaoxing.

386
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:32,840
Okay.

387
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,480
I happen to have work to do.

388
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,000
Good luck on your own.

389
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:39,960
Yeah.

390
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:49,770
Xu Xiao, do you want a popsicle?

391
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:51,760
No, thanks.

392
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:53,500
Xu Xiao,

393
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,280
how come you thought of

394
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,940
asking me to visit here today?

395
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,280
A friend gave me two tickets.

396
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:00,640
Since you were free,

397
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,040
I asked you to come along.

398
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:02,760
Really?

399
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,359
I haven't been here before either.

400
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:06,290
I can have a good look around today.

401
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:07,569
Let's go.

402
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,520
It's over 80 hectares.

403
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:11,480
It'll take a whole day to walk around.

404
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:11,920
Okay.

405
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,359
Are you sure you don't want it?

406
00:17:13,359 --> 00:17:13,920
No.

407
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:14,680
Then I'll eat them all.

408
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:15,540
Let's hurry up,

409
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:17,569
or we won't finish looking around.

410
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,089
These buildings are so beautiful.

411
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:21,319
Look, Xu Xiao.

412
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:22,720
Look at that one up there.

413
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,650
What does it say?

414
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:30,640
Xu Xiao!

415
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:32,640
Wait for me!

416
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,280
Okay.

417
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,920
Look, it's so beautiful over there.

418
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,500
The environment here is really nice.

419
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,740
Xu Xiao, can I tell you something?

420
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:01,320
Sorry.

421
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,080
I really can't hold it in anymore.

422
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:05,560
I was originally going to tell Wang Lin all this,

423
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,360
but as for this matter,

424
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:08,090
I don't know what to do anymore.

425
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,560
What is it?

426
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,220
Did you know

427
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,930
that Wang Lin and Xiaoyi got together before?

428
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,010
You didn't know?

429
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:17,050
I didn't.

430
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,520
Back then,

431
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:21,600
the whole class knew Wang Lin confessed to Wu Jing.

432
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:23,320
Wang Lin felt he lost face,

433
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:26,080
then Xiaoyi comforted him.

434
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:28,770
He took the opportunity to confess to Xiaoyi,

435
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:30,140
and they got together.

436
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,520
But later on,

437
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:35,320
Xiaoyi broke up with Wang Lin.

438
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,560
Maybe these two failures

439
00:18:43,120 --> 00:18:45,180
made Wang Lin unwilling to accept it.

440
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:48,400
He kept going to Xiaoyi over and over to get back together.

441
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,640
Xiaoyi doesn't really know how to reject people,

442
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,240
so she didn't know what to do.

443
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,920
She knew I had a good relationship with Wang Lin,

444
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,000
so she came to me.

445
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:58,920
She originally wanted me to talk sense into Wang Lin,

446
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,850
to persuade him.

447
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,460
But I didn't expect...

448
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,460
Are you listening?

449
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:04,680
I am.

450
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:07,930
I didn't expect that over time,

451
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,680
the relationship between me and Xiaoyi

452
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,280
seems to have changed too.

453
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,440
Don't get me wrong,

454
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:15,500
there's nothing going on between us.

455
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,120
It's just that after hanging out more,

456
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:19,080
I found we have a lot in common.

457
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:21,480
I'm telling you, don't disbelieve me.

458
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:24,280
We were born on the exact same day, month, and year.

459
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:25,320
We're both Aries.

460
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,520
I like sports,

461
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:28,120
and she likes sports too.

462
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,760
We both really like playing video games.

463
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:33,320
Anyway, we just have a lot in common.

464
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:35,840
At this point,

465
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,400
you've probably figured it out, right?

466
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:42,640
I...

467
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:44,370
I've fallen for Xiaoyi.

468
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,560
I originally thought

469
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:52,020
he would talk a little less than Wang Lin.

470
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:56,240
Xiaoxing.

471
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,760
You can't do it like this.

472
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:58,960
You have to follow...

473
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:00,640
I can make it whatever

474
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,640
I want it to be.

475
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,730
That won't work.

476
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:03,860
You have to listen.

477
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:05,360
Let me tell you,

478
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:06,920
an artwork

479
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,400
best reflects a person's heart.

480
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:12,640
A good work must come from a good mind.

481
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:14,400
For example, if you are a good kid,

482
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:16,320
the things you make will definitely be beautiful.

483
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:17,160
If you don't listen,

484
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:19,020
the things you make will look bad.

485
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:22,240
I love communicating with kids.

486
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:23,120
As for kids,

487
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:25,820
they need to be educated from a young age, right?

488
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:28,400
What shape are you making?

489
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,280
Look at mine.

490
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,160
I can make whatever I want.

491
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:34,740
Look at you.

492
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:36,280
Play by yourself.

493
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,520
Need a hand?

494
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:47,820
No, I can handle it myself.

495
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,380
Your kid is quite naughty.

496
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:50,160
Yes.

497
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,000
He's been mischievous since he was little.

498
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,040
It's good to be naughty.

499
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:54,170
It means he's smart.

500
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,930
You shouldn't push so hard.

501
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,570
Be a bit gentler.

502
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:01,000
Right, right, right.

503
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,320
I'll do it myself. I'll do it. No need.

504
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,320
I can do it myself.

505
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:05,680
Have you seen a movie called

506
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,640
'Ghost'?

507
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:07,360
No.

508
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,060
It's a very classic movie.

509
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:11,840
The most classic scene in it

510
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:14,640
is the male and female leads making pottery together.

511
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,770
You haven't seen it?

512
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:19,840
Let me tell you, it's very romantic.

513
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:21,840
How is it done?

514
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:22,520
Like this.

515
00:21:22,840 --> 00:21:24,440
Gently hug the female lead

516
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,800
from behind.

517
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:26,680
No, no need.

518
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:27,320
It's fine. It's fine.

519
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,120
No need, it's fine.

520
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,120
No need, Mr. Zhang.

521
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:30,080
I can do it myself.

522
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:30,520
You, you...

523
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:31,320
You should go back to your seat.

524
00:21:31,320 --> 00:21:32,000
You might not be able to.

525
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:32,720
I can do it myself.

526
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,960
No, you don't understand this.

527
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,000
This is very inconvenient for me.

528
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:36,240
This requires professional knowledge.

529
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:36,920
Mr. Zhang, could you go back to your seat?

530
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:38,640
I have formally studied this, listen to me.

531
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,640
I can do it myself.

532
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:40,320
Really.

533
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:43,760
What are you doing, you little bastard?

534
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:45,410
Who are you cursing?

535
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,120
Okay.

536
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,320
I was joking.

537
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:53,160
How could I stoop to a child's level?

538
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,170
Are you okay?

539
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:56,090
I'm fine.

540
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,010
Come, let me see.

541
00:21:59,240 --> 00:21:59,840
Mr. Zhang,

542
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,600
how is it going?

543
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:03,700
I brought water. Come, have some.

544
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:04,840
Ms. Liu.

545
00:22:05,760 --> 00:22:07,420
How did you get it on your face?

546
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,440
I just remembered I have something to do.

547
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,370
I'm leaving now.

548
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:12,520
Mr. Zhang,

549
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,120
that's so sudden.

550
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:22,160
Let me see.

551
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:26,820
Apologize.

552
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,480
I won't apologize.

553
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:30,010
I didn't do anything wrong.

554
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:31,920
You kid.

555
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,440
Why are you so insensible?

556
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:33,960
Sis.

557
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,760
There's something wrong with that guy.

558
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:37,690
There is something wrong with him.

559
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:38,880
The child is immature.

560
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,080
Are you immature too?

561
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:41,240
I go out for a while,

562
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,760
and things turn out like this.

563
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:43,890
At the end of the day,

564
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,450
should a child hit someone?

565
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:46,720
How many times have I told you?

566
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,850
You can't spoil him.

567
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,000
Him being like this today,

568
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,060
I'm telling you, it's all your fault.

569
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,080
I don't like him.

570
00:22:52,080 --> 00:22:53,200
My mom doesn't like him either.

571
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:54,520
We just don't want to know him.

572
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,920
I'm telling you, I'm doing this for your own good.

573
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,780
For your mother's good, you know?

574
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:58,600
No, you're not.

575
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:00,520
Aunt, you force me to do extracurricular homework every day.

576
00:23:00,520 --> 00:23:02,240
Now you're making my mom meet a new uncle.

577
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,040
I hate you.

578
00:23:03,560 --> 00:23:04,160
Xiaoxing.

579
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,570
Why are you here?

580
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:06,820
Get out of my house.

581
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,640
I hate you.

582
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:10,000
You can't talk to your aunt like that.

583
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,960
Apologize to your aunt.

584
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:11,760
I won't apologize.

585
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:12,400
Xiaoxing.

586
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,010
It's okay. Let's go.

587
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:04,300
Come in.

588
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,570
Xiaocen.

589
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:08,000
Aunt.

590
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:12,200
Come here.

591
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,040
Have a seat.

592
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:16,520
Aunt,

593
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,160
don't be sad.

594
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,210
My mom is just like that.

595
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:22,520
It's fine.

596
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:25,800
I know she means well.

597
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:27,730
As for me,

598
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,770
I'm much younger than your mom.

599
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:31,960
When we were little,

600
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,840
your grandparents were busy with work,

601
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:35,480
so your mom was the one taking care of me.

602
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:36,600
So, just like you,

603
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:39,040
I listened to her about everything.

604
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:40,880
It's just that

605
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,560
my previous failed marriage

606
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:47,040
has made me lose confidence in many things.

607
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:48,680
Currently,

608
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:52,360
I don't want to start a new life.

609
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:55,920
Aunt, I understand you.

610
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:59,850
I understand your mom, too.

611
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,760
Xiaoxing is still young.

612
00:25:03,320 --> 00:25:05,800
He's grown up without a father around.

613
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:09,650
I failed to give him a complete family,

614
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,330
and I feel really sorry for him.

615
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:16,160
But look, Xiaoxing is very happy now.

616
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,000
A bad marriage

617
00:25:18,280 --> 00:25:20,040
won't bring him happiness.

618
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:22,920
Aunt, you're already doing great.

619
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:26,080
You've raised Xiaoxing to be so excellent.

620
00:25:26,080 --> 00:25:27,320
He's like a little man,

621
00:25:27,320 --> 00:25:28,720
even more mature than me.

622
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:31,050
You've already done very well.

623
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,530
Thank you, Xiaocen.

624
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,940
You're great, too.

625
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:38,560
Don't be sad.

626
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:40,880
Don't be.

627
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:41,840
Having you all by my side

628
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:42,880
makes me very happy.
